<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Set-Cookie header class is missing two setters in its constructor, path and httponly. The following fixes this:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
+ if ($path) {
+     $this-&gt;setPath($path);
+ }

  if ($secure) {
      $this-&gt;setSecure($secure);
  }

+ if ($httponly) {
+     $this-&gt;setHttponly($httponly);
+ }
</code></pre>

